425
00:32:29,446 --> 00:32:32,677
Hey, whatever happens...

426
00:32:33,718 --> 00:32:34,844
I will marry you.

427
00:32:40,223 --> 00:32:43,125
When the summer holiday arrives,
let's meet here.

428
00:33:03,681 --> 00:33:05,706
Asa, I have something to tell you.

