435
00:34:15,952 --> 00:34:17,181
Please don't.

436
00:34:18,556 --> 00:34:20,079
Shit.

437
00:34:20,224 --> 00:34:22,249
Asa! Asa!

438
00:34:25,463 --> 00:34:26,725
Please don't!

439
00:34:26,831 --> 00:34:28,025
Stay quiet.

440
00:34:31,268 --> 00:34:32,292
Please don't!

441
00:34:35,239 --> 00:34:36,398
Wait.

