00:34:40,577 --> 00:34:41,737
Asa.

443
00:34:44,181 --> 00:34:45,546
Please don't!

444
00:34:57,961 --> 00:34:59,121
Idiot!

445
00:35:08,706 --> 00:35:09,900
Asa.

446
00:35:24,889 --> 00:35:26,652
Please don't.

447
00:35:26,791 --> 00:35:28,280
Young master!

